{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Memoirium, everything is but sand and stars.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Locations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/memlocations.gif?t=1736567256\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The realm of dreams does not abide by any rules or genre. In one moment, you will find yourself in a simple 21st-century school, and in the next, your eyes will fall upon a castle held together by wax.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Masks and more</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/equipment.gif?t=1736567256\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Most, if not all, of the equipment will alter yourself and the entities you encounter. One piece of armor can affect how long negative statuses last, while a specific mask will change how enemies approach you in combat.\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Consumed now but not forever.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/itemheal.gif?t=1736567256\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All of the items you find will not disappear when you use them. Instead, consumables are fully replenished at certain points in your journey. Finding the same item will upgrade it, but only until a certain point.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your room</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There also appears to be a mysterious location that you have control of in the dream world.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3294440?t=1736567256","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3294440?t=1736567256","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/475c3ba549a6e224bd75d10825b9f2499ed2730a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736567256","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/475c3ba549a6e224bd75d10825b9f2499ed2730a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736567256","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Memoirium, everything is but sand and stars.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Locations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/memlocations.gif?t=1736567256\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The realm of dreams does not abide by any rules or genre. In one moment, you will find yourself in a simple 21st-century school, and in the next, your eyes will fall upon a castle held together by wax.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Masks and more</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/equipment.gif?t=1736567256\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Most, if not all, of the equipment will alter yourself and the entities you encounter. One piece of armor can affect how long negative statuses last, while a specific mask will change how enemies approach you in combat.\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Consumed now but not forever.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/itemheal.gif?t=1736567256\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All of the items you find will not disappear when you use them. Instead, consumables are fully replenished at certain points in your journey. Finding the same item will upgrade it, but only until a certain point.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your room</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There also appears to be a mysterious location that you have control of in the dream world.</p>","developers":["GoldenGratus"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/header.jpg?t=1736567256","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257084803,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257084803/movie480.mp4?t=1736567166","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257084803/movie_max.mp4?t=1736567166"},"name":"Stream Gameplay Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257084803/9cd62edf445f65ad550e948325d4196aba029dd7/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1736567166","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257084803/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1736567166","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257084803/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1736567166"}}],"name":"Memoirium","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel or AMD Dual Core<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVIDIA GTX 970<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 500 MB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</li></ul>"},"platforms":{"linux":false,"mac":false,"windows":true},"publishers":["GoldenGratus","Outersloth"],"ratings":{"dejus":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Viol\u00